| WC4 || C<small>{{thinsp}}IV</small>強烈，C<small>{{thinsp}}II</small>微弱， O<small>{{thinsp}}V</small>溫和 || C<small>{{thinsp}}IV</small>/C<small>{{thinsp}}III</small> > 32 || O<small>{{thinsp}}V</small>/C<small>{{thinsp}}III</small> > 2.5 || O<small>{{thinsp}}VI</small>微弱或缺乏
