| WC9 || C<small>{{thinsp}}III</small> > C<small>{{thinsp}}IV</small>，缺乏C<small>{{thinsp}}II</small>, O<small>{{thinsp}}V</small>微弱或缺乏 || 0.2 < C<small>{{thinsp}}IV</small>/C<small>{{thinsp}}III</small> < 0.5 || 0.6 < C<small>{{thinsp}}IV</small>/C<small>{{thinsp}}II</small> < 10 || 0.15 < He<small>{{thinsp}}II</small>/He<small>{{thinsp}}I</small> < 1.25
|-
| WC10 || || 0.06 < C<small>{{thinsp}}IV</small>/C<small>{{thinsp}}III</small> < 0.15 || 0.03 < C<small>{{thinsp}}IV</small>/C<small>{{thinsp}}II</small> < 0.6 || He<small>{{thinsp}}II</small>/He<small>{{thinsp}}I</small> < 0.15
|-
| WC11 || || C<small>{{thinsp}}IV</small>/C<small>{{thinsp}}III</small> < 0.06 || C<small>{{thinsp}}IV</small>/C<small>{{thinsp}}II</small> < 0.03 || 缺乏He<small>{{thinsp}}II</small>
|}

WO型的恆星主要依據C<small>{{thinsp}}IV</small>的580.1 奈米、O<small>{{thinsp}}IV</small>的340.0 奈米、O<small>{{thinsp}}V</small>（和 O<small>{{thinsp}}III</small>）混合557.2–559.8 奈米、O<small>{{thinsp}}VI</small>的381.1–383.4 奈米、O<small>{{thinsp}}VII</small>的567.0 奈米、和 O<small>{{thinsp}}VIII</small>在606.8 奈米譜線來分類。這個序列並基於O<small>{{thinsp}}VI</small>/C<small>{{thinsp}}IV</small>和O<small>{{thinsp}}VI</small>/O<small>{{thinsp}}V</small>線的相對強度，擴展至包括WO5<ref name=kingsburgh>{{cite journal|bibcode=1995A&A...295...75K|title=Properties of the WO Wolf–Rayet stars|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_astronomy-and-astrophysics_1995-03_295_1/page/75|journal=Astronomy and Astrophysics |issn=0004-6361|volume=295|pages=75|last1=Kingsburgh|first1=R. L.|last2=Barlow|first2=M. J.|last3=Storey|first3=P. J.|year=1995}}</ref>。後來設計用於使傳統的沃夫–瑞葉星和行星狀星雲中心星一致，返回到WO1至WO4序列，並調整了分區<ref name=WCO/>。

